{"type":null,"faqId":45311,"title":"用荣耀盒子M321看视频很卡或缓冲很慢怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.7715278in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.7715278in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.009722223in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>一般是网速不够导致节目播放卡顿。请参考如下方式进行解决：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>进入“</span><span class=\"s2\">设置 &gt; 网络 &gt; 网络测速</span><span>”检测您的网速，并根据测速结果选择播放对应清晰度的视频。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>提前将想看的视频添加至“</span><span class=\"s2\">我的缓存</span><span>”，待视频缓存一部分后再观看。已缓存的视频内容不会卡。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>参考如下方式改善网络环境：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">−  </span><span>清理内存。按一下遥控器待机键 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164837\" style=\"width:0.34652779in;height:0.3048611in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，选择“</span><span class=\"s2\">内存清理</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">−  </span><span>用网线连接路由器上网，网速会更稳定。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">−  </span><span>如使用Wi-Fi 上网，请确保盒子和路由器之间没有大的障碍物，建议将盒子放在距路由器1~3米的范围内。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">−  </span><span>暂停其他设备中占据网络流量较高的任务，如下载、游戏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">−  </span><span>更换更高的网络带宽。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">−  </span><span>如果您使用的是小运营商提供的网络带宽服务，可能是运营商劫持了央广银河服务器，请致电运营商，要求解除劫持。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164838\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":244,"faqType":"在线播放","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"832","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Online-Play","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556872000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":21,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"视频卡,卡顿,慢,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}